VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'whatever you want to do. Links in the description below. All right. Now, here is the research paper. Also, we\'ll link this down below. So we present Surfer H, a cost-efficient web agent that integrates vision language models. We pair it with Hollow One, which is a new'

