VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'versus the hollow 17B. And as you can see, almost across the board, the Hollow 3B wins. Same with the Hollow 7B. It just outperforms the other ones. And the'

[07:38] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'overall average, as you can see, is pretty substantially higher than the rest of the models on the list for the 3 billion parameter version. For the 7 billion parameter version, it has a nice win over the U ground V1. And so the'

